	(text "First honest front-door capture for `P1`.\nThis is a passive provisional summer: `CV_IN` dominates, `COARSE_TUNE` and `FINE_TUNE` add smaller offsets, and `TUNE_SUM` is easy to probe."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 38.1 111.76 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "66666666-6666-6666-8666-000000000002")
	)
	(text "Weighting is intentionally provisional.\nThe goal here is to stop lying about the front door, not to lock final panel law or calibration strategy."
